{{redir|CMIS|the computer networking standard for a service that may be employed by network elements for network management|Common management information service}}
{{external links|date=July 2015}}
{{Infobox file format
| name = CMIS
| icon = [[File:Cmis logo.png|200px]]
| extension =
| mime =
| owner =
| creatorcode =
| genre = [[Enterprise content management]]
| containerfor =
| containedby =
| extendedfrom = [[SOAP]]
| extendedto =
