In 1995, on the occasion of the 100th [[anniversary]] of cinema, the [[Holy See|Vatican]] compiled a list of 45 "great films". The 45 movies are divided into three categories: religion, values, and art.
==Religion== {{div col}} * ''[[Andrei Rublev (film)|Andrei Rublev]]'' (1966) * ''[[Babette's Feast]]'' (1987) * ''[[Ben-Hur (1959 film)|Ben-Hur]]'' (1959) * ''[[The Flowers of St. Francis]]'' (1950) * ''[[Francesco (film)|Francesco]]'' (1989) * ''[[The Gospel According to St. Matthew (film)|The Gospel According to St. Matthew]]'' (1966) * ''[[Vie et Passion du Christ|La Passion de Notre Seigneur Jesus-Christ]]'' (1905) * ''[[A Man for All Seasons (1966 film)|A Man for All Seasons]]'' (1966) * ''[[The Mission (1986 film)|The Mission]]'' (1986) * ''[[Monsieur Vincent]]'' (1947) * ''[[Nazarin]]'' (1958) * ''[[Ordet]]'' (1955) * ''[[The Passion of Joan of Arc]]'' (1928) * ''[[The Sacrifice]]'' (1986) * ''[[Thérèse (film)|Therese]]'' (1986) {{div col end}}
==Values== {{div col}} * ''[[Au Revoir les Enfants]]'' (1988) * ''[[Bicycle Thieves]]'' (1949) * ''[[The Burmese Harp (1956 film)|The Burmese Harp]]'' (1956) * ''[[Chariots of Fire]]'' (1981) * ''[[Dekalog]]'' (1988) * ''[[Dersu Uzala (1975 film)|Dersu Uzala]]'' (1975) * ''[[Gandhi (film)|Gandhi]]'' (1982) * ''[[Intolerance (film)|Intolerance]]'' (1916) * ''[[It's a Wonderful Life]]'' (1946) * ''[[On the Waterfront]]'' (1954) * ''[[Rome, Open City]]'' (1945) * ''[[Schindler's List]]'' (1993) * ''[[The Seventh Seal]]'' (1957) * ''[[The Tree of Wooden Clogs]]'' (1978) * ''[[Wild Strawberries (film)|Wild Strawberries]]'' (1957) {{div col end}}
==Art== {{div col}} * ''[[Citizen Kane]]'' (1941) * ''[[8½]]'' (1963) * ''[[Fantasia (1940 film)|Fantasia]]'' (1940) * ''[[Grand Illusion (film)|Grand Illusion]]'' (1937) * ''[[La strada|La Strada]]'' (1954) * ''[[The Lavender Hill Mob]]'' (1951) * ''[[The Leopard (1963 film)|The Leopard]]'' (1963) * ''[[Little Women (1933 film)|Little Women]]'' (1933) * ''[[Metropolis (1927 film)|Metropolis]]'' (1927) * ''[[Modern Times (film)|Modern Times]]'' (1936) * ''[[Napoleon (1927 film)|Napoleon]]'' (1927) * ''[[Nosferatu]]'' (1922) * ''[[Stagecoach (1939 film)|Stagecoach]]'' (1939) * ''[[2001: A Space Odyssey (film)|2001: A Space Odyssey]]'' (1968) * ''[[The Wizard of Oz (1939 film)|The Wizard of Oz]]'' (1939) {{div col end}}
